: ''Not to be confused with [[Cailin Praytor]] or [[Caitlin]].''

'''Cailin''' is [[Ross Geller|Ross]]'s date whom he brings to watch [[Joey Tribbiani|Joey]]'s play in "[[The One With The Screamer]]". Unfortunately Ross focuses more on  [[Tommy]], [[Rachel Greene|Rachel]]'s date after he screams at an elderly couple sitting in their seats.

Cailin is played by [[Laura Cayouette]] who is best known for Django Unchained, Enemy of the State and Hell Ride.
